cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.HC, cs.MA 

This paper discusses the security and privacy threats posed by power side channels on mobile devices, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR), system and control (cs.SY), software engineering (cs.SE), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and machine learning (cs.MA). However, since the focus of the paper is on security and privacy, cs.CR is the most likely category, followed by cs.SY and cs.SE.
